#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.6:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Dhanavagga"
msgstr "1. Wealth"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Vitthatadhanasutta"
msgstr "6. Wealth in Detail"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:1.1"
msgid "“Sattimāni, bhikkhave, dhanāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these seven kinds of wealth."

msgctxt "an7.6:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.6:1.3"
msgid ""
"Saddhādhanaṃ, sīladhanaṃ, hirīdhanaṃ, ottappadhanaṃ, sutadhanaṃ, cāgadhanaṃ, "
"paññādhanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The wealth of faith, ethical conduct, conscience, prudence, learning, "
"generosity, and wisdom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, saddhādhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of faith?"

msgctxt "an7.6:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako saddho hoti, saddahati tathāgatassa bodhiṃ:"
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple has faith in the Realized One’s awakening …"

msgctxt "an7.6:2.3"
msgid "‘itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho … pe … buddho bhagavā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.6:2.4"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, saddhādhanaṃ. (1)"
msgstr "This is called the wealth of faith."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, sīladhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of ethical conduct?"

msgctxt "an7.6:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti … pe … "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, commit "
"sexual misconduct, use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical, "
"or consume alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "an7.6:3.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sīladhanaṃ. (2)"
msgstr "This is called the wealth of ethical conduct."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:4.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, hirīdhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of conscience?"

msgctxt "an7.6:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako hirīmā hoti, hirīyati kāyaduccaritena "
"vacīduccaritena manoduccaritena, hirīyati pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"samāpattiyā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple has a conscience. They’re conscientious about bad "
"conduct by way of body, speech, and mind, and conscientious about having any "
"bad, unskillful qualities."

msgctxt "an7.6:4.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, hirīdhanaṃ. (3)"
msgstr "This is called the wealth of conscience."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:5.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, ottappadhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of prudence?"

msgctxt "an7.6:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako ottappī hoti, ottappati kāyaduccaritena "
"vacīduccaritena manoduccaritena, ottappati pāpakānaṃ akusalānaṃ dhammānaṃ "
"samāpattiyā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple is prudent. They’re prudent when it comes to bad "
"conduct by way of body, speech, and mind, and prudent when it comes to the "
"acquiring of any bad, unskillful qualities."

msgctxt "an7.6:5.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, ottappadhanaṃ. (4)"
msgstr "This is called the wealth of prudence."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.6"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:6.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, sutadhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of learning?"

msgctxt "an7.6:6.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako bahussuto hoti sutadharo sutasannicayo. Ye te "
"dhammā ādikalyāṇā majjhekalyāṇā pariyosānakalyāṇā sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ "
"kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ abhivadanti. Tathārūpāssa dhammā "
"bahussutā honti dhātā vacasā paricitā manasānupekkhitā diṭṭhiyā "
"suppaṭividdhā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple is very learned, remembering and keeping what "
"they’ve learned. These teachings are good in the beginning, good in the "
"middle, and good in the end, meaningful and well-phrased, describing a "
"spiritual practice that’s entirely full and pure. They are very learned in "
"such teachings, remembering them, reciting them, mentally scrutinizing them, "
"and comprehending them theoretically."

msgctxt "an7.6:6.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sutadhanaṃ. (5)"
msgstr "This is called the wealth of learning."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:7.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, cāgadhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of generosity?"

msgctxt "an7.6:7.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati "
"muttacāgo payatapāṇi vosaggarato yācayogo dānasaṃvibhāgarato."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple lives at home rid of the stain of stinginess, "
"freely generous, open-handed, loving to let go, committed to charity, loving "
"to give and to share."

msgctxt "an7.6:7.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, cāgadhanaṃ. (6)"
msgstr "This is called the wealth of generosity."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:8.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, paññādhanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is the wealth of wisdom?"

msgctxt "an7.6:8.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako paññavā hoti … pe … sammā dukkhakkhayagāminiyā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple is wise. They have the wisdom of arising and "
"passing away which is noble, penetrative, and leads to the complete ending "
"of suffering."

msgctxt "an7.6:8.3"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, paññādhanaṃ. (7)"
msgstr "This is called the wealth of wisdom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:9.1"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, sattadhanānīti."
msgstr "These are the seven kinds of wealth.”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:10.1"
msgid "Saddhādhanaṃ sīladhanaṃ,"
msgstr "“Faith and ethical conduct are kinds of wealth,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.6:10.2"
msgid "hirī ottappiyaṃ dhanaṃ;"
msgstr "as are conscience and prudence,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.6:10.3"
msgid "Sutadhanañca cāgo ca,"
msgstr "learning and generosity,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.6:10.4"
msgid "paññā ve sattamaṃ dhanaṃ."
msgstr "and wisdom is the seventh kind of wealth."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:11.1"
msgid "Yassa ete dhanā atthi,"
msgstr "When a woman or man"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.6:11.2"
msgid "itthiyā purisassa vā;"
msgstr "has these kinds of wealth,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.6:11.3"
msgid "Adaliddoti taṃ āhu,"
msgstr "they’re said to be prosperous,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.6:11.4"
msgid "amoghaṃ tassa jīvitaṃ."
msgstr "their life is not in vain."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an7.6:12.1"
msgid "Tasmā saddhañca sīlañca,"
msgstr "So let the wise devote themselves"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.6:12.2"
msgid "pasādaṃ dhammadassanaṃ;"
msgstr "to faith, ethical behaviour,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.6:12.3"
msgid "Anuyuñjetha medhāvī,"
msgstr "confidence, and insight into the teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an7.6:12.4"
msgid "saraṃ buddhāna sāsanan”ti."
msgstr "remembering the instructions of the Buddhas.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.6:12.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
